      "generation": {
        "prompt": "",
        "config": {}
      },
      "html": "\n<section x-data=\"{ \n    selectedIndex: 0,\n    faqs: [\n        { q: 'What stages do you invest in?', a: 'We invest from Pre-Seed through Series B and beyond, depending on the opportunity. Our primary focus is on early-stage founders demonstrating strong PMF or solving high-complexity problems.' },\n        { q: 'Do you invest outside India?', a: 'Yes, we invest globally with a focus on emerging markets and high-growth regions. Our network spans multiple continents to help founders scale internationally.' },\n        { q: 'How long does the process take?', a: 'From application to term sheet typically takes 3–6 weeks depending on due diligence. We pride ourselves on being fast, transparent, and respectful of a founder's time.' },\n        { q: 'What equity stake do you take?', a: 'We typically take 5–15% equity, negotiated based on stage and valuation. We aim to be a meaningful partner without being overly dilutive to the founding team.' },\n        { q: 'Do you lead rounds?', a: 'We can lead or co-invest depending on the deal structure and existing cap table. We are comfortable setting terms or joining as a strategic value-add partner.' },\n        { q: 'What do you look for in a founder?', a: 'Resilience, domain expertise, coachability, and a clear vision for the problem being solved. We back people first, knowing that the journey will have many pivots.' }\n    ],\n    showTopGradient: false,\n    showBottomGradient: true,\n    handleScroll(e) {\n        const { scrollTop, scrollHeight, clientHeight } = e.target;\n        this.showTopGradient = scrollTop > 20;\n        this.showBottomGradient = scrollHeight - (scrollTop + clientHeight) > 20;\n    }\n}\" class=\"w-full min-h-[900px] bg-[#05020d] py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 flex items-center justify-center font-sans overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"0\">\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden pointer-events-none\" data-kid=\"1\">\n        <div class=\"absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-purple-900/20 blur-[120px] rounded-full\" data-kid=\"2\"></div>\n        <div class=\"absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-cyan-900/20 blur-[120px] rounded-full\" data-kid=\"3\"></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl w-full relative z-10\" data-kid=\"4\">\n        \n        <div class=\"mb-20 text-center lg:text-left\" data-kid=\"5\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-none\" data-kid=\"6\">\n                Decoding <span class=\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-blue-500 to-purple-600\" data-kid=\"7\">The Partnership.</span>\n            </h2>\n            <p class=\"text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl\" data-kid=\"8\">\n                Transparency is our core value. Here's everything you need to know about how we build the future together.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-start\" data-kid=\"9\">\n            \n            \n            <div class=\"lg:col-span-5 relative h-[600px] flex flex-col\" data-kid=\"10\">\n                \n                <div x-show=\"showTopGradient\" x-transition:enter=\"transition opacity-300\" x-transition:enter-start=\"opacity-0\" x-transition:enter-end=\"opacity-100\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#05020d] to-transparent z-20 pointer-events-none\" data-kid=\"11\">\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div @scroll=\"handleScroll\" class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto pr-4 space-y-4 custom-scrollbar relative z-10\" style=\"scrollbar-gutter: stable;\" data-kid=\"12\">\n                    \n                    <template x-for=\"(faq, index) in faqs\" :key=\"index\" data-kid=\"13\">\n                        <div @mouseenter=\"selectedIndex = index\" @click=\"selectedIndex = index\" class=\"group cursor-pointer relative\" :class=\"selectedIndex === index ? 'scale-[1.02]' : 'scale-100 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100'\" style=\"transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);\" data-kid=\"14\">\n                            \n                            \n                            <div class=\"p-6 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-md transition-all duration-300 border\" :class=\"selectedIndex === index ? 'bg-white/15 border-white/20 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(34,211,238,0.15)]' : 'bg-white/5 border-white/5 hover:border-white/10'\" data-kid=\"15\">\n                                \n                                <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4\" data-kid=\"16\">\n                                    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold transition-colors duration-300\" :class=\"selectedIndex === index ? 'text-white' : 'text-slate-400 group-hover:text-white'\" x-text=\"faq.q\" data-kid=\"17\">\n                                    </h3>\n                                    \n                                    <div class=\"shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300\" :class=\"selectedIndex === index ? 'bg-cyan-500 text-white scale-110' : 'bg-white/5 text-slate-500 group-hover:bg-white/10'\" data-kid=\"18\">\n                                        <i class=\"ph-bold ph-caret-right text-sm\" data-kid=\"19\"></i>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            \n                            <div x-show=\"selectedIndex === index\" class=\"absolute -left-1 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-1.5 h-10 bg-cyan-400 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(34,211,238,0.8)]\" x-transition:enter=\"transition scale-y-0 opacity-0 duration-300\" x-transition:enter-start=\"scale-y-0 opacity-0\" x-transition:enter-end=\"scale-y-100 opacity-100\" data-kid=\"20\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </template>\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div x-show=\"showBottomGradient\" x-transition:enter=\"transition opacity-300\" x-transition:enter-start=\"opacity-0\" x-transition:enter-end=\"opacity-100\" class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-24 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#05020d] to-transparent z-20 pointer-events-none\" data-kid=\"21\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            \n            <div class=\"lg:col-span-7\" data-kid=\"22\">\n                <div class=\"relative h-[600px] rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-white/[0.08] to-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden group\" data-kid=\"23\">\n                    \n                    \n                    <div class=\"absolute -top-1/4 -right-1/4 w-3/4 h-3/4 bg-cyan-500/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110\" data-kid=\"24\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"absolute -bottom-1/4 -left-1/4 w-3/4 h-3/4 bg-purple-500/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110\" data-kid=\"25\"></div>\n\n                    \n                    <div class=\"relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-center p-10 md:p-16\" data-kid=\"26\">\n                        <div class=\"mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"27\">\n                            <span class=\"w-12 h-[1px] bg-cyan-400/50\" data-kid=\"28\"></span>\n                            <span class=\"text-cyan-400 text-xs font-black tracking-[0.2em] uppercase\" data-kid=\"29\">Detailed Response</span>\n                        </div>\n\n                        \n                        <div class=\"min-h-[120px] mb-8\" data-kid=\"30\">\n                            <h3 x-text=\"faqs[selectedIndex].q\" class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.1]\" x-transition:enter=\"transition transform duration-500\" x-transition:enter-start=\"translate-y-4 opacity-0\" x-transition:enter-end=\"translate-y-0 opacity-100\" data-kid=\"31\">\n                            </h3>\n                        </div>\n\n                        \n                        <div class=\"space-y-8\" data-kid=\"32\">\n                            <div class=\"h-1.5 w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"33\"></div>\n                            \n                            <p x-text=\"faqs[selectedIndex].a\" class=\"text-slate-300 text-lg md:text-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium\" x-transition:enter=\"transition transform delay-100 duration-500\" x-transition:enter-start=\"translate-y-4 opacity-0\" x-transition:enter-end=\"translate-y-0 opacity-100\" data-kid=\"34\">\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n\n                        \n                        <div class=\"mt-12 flex items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"35\">\n                            <button class=\"px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#05020d] font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-cyan-400 hover:text-[#05020d] transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-3 group/btn cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"36\">\n                                Learn More Process\n                                <i class=\"ph-bold ph-arrow-right transition-transform group-hover/btn:translate-x-1\" data-kid=\"37\"></i>\n                            </button>\n                            <button class=\"text-white/60 hover:text-white font-semibold transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"38\">\n                                Share this FAQ\n                                <i class=\"ph ph-share-network\" data-kid=\"39\"></i>\n                            </button>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <style data-kid=\"40\">\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');\n        \n        :root {\n            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        /* Custom Scrollbar */\n        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {\n            width: 4px;\n        }\n        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n        }\n        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            transition: all 0.3s;\n        }\n        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        /* Prevent layout shift when scrollbar appears */\n        .scrollbar-gutter-stable {\n            scrollbar-gutter: stable;\n        }\n\n        /* Animation utilities */\n        [x-cloak] { display: none !important; }\n    </style>\n\n    \n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js\" defer data-kid=\"41\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/@phosphor-icons/web\" data-kid=\"42\"></script>\n</section>\n",
